      "start": 359.23,
      "end": 360.17,
      "text": "먼저 듣고 올게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.17,
      "end": 384.22,
      "text": "Oh, Teresa"
    },
    {
      "start": 384.22,
      "end": 385.8,
      "text": "오스가 asked Isabel"
    },
    {
      "start": 385.8,
      "end": 387.0,
      "text": "to come by her house"
    },
    {
      "start": 387.0,
      "end": 388.04,
      "text": "when she was gone"
    },
    {
      "start": 388.04,
      "end": 390.0,
      "text": "to her mother's house"
    },
    {
      "start": 390.0,
      "end": 390.94,
      "text": "Oh, come over"
    },
    {
      "start": 390.94,
      "end": 394.34,
      "text": "네, 자신의 쌍둥이 아들들을 데리고"
    },
    {
      "start": 394.34,
      "end": 396.3,
      "text": "나는 친정에 가 있을 테니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.3,
      "end": 397.26,
      "text": "내가 없을 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 397.26,
      "end": 400.06,
      "text": "Isabel, 당신이 우리 집에 와가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 400.06,
      "end": 401.74,
      "text": "남편하고 좀 이야기를 해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 401.74,
      "end": 403.04,
      "text": "라고 이야기를 했었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.04,
      "end": 403.74,
      "text": "억울하시네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.74,
      "end": 405.06,
      "text": "Talk to him"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.06,
      "end": 406.12,
      "text": "Work it out"
    },
    {
      "start": 406.12,
      "end": 407.68,
      "text": "Work everything out"
    },
    {
      "start": 407.68,
      "end": 409.46,
      "text": "You have a lot of issues between you"
    },
    {
      "start": 409.46,
      "end": 410.48,
      "text": "Work it out"
    },
    {
      "start": 410.48,
      "end": 412.16,
      "text": "그래서 Isabel이 정말"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.16,
      "end": 413.24,
      "text": "집에 와가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 413.24,
      "end": 415.48,
      "text": "오스카하고 대화를 하는 장면이었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 415.48,
      "end": 417.76,
      "text": "근데 이 장면의 바로 전에"
    },
    {
      "start": 417.76,
      "end": 419.66,
      "text": "왜 테리사가"
    },
    {
      "start": 419.66,
      "end": 421.42,
      "text": "2천만 달러"
    },
    {
      "start": 421.42,
      "end": 422.72,
      "text": "240억 원이나"
    },
    {
      "start": 422.72,
      "end": 423.88,
      "text": "기부를 한다고 하는지"
    },
    {
      "start": 423.88,
      "end": 425.46,
      "text": "나는 도통 이해할 수가 없어"
    },
    {
      "start": 425.46,
      "end": 426.88,
      "text": "도대체 꽁꽁이가 뭐야"
    },
    {
      "start": 426.88,
      "end": 427.78,
      "text": "라는 의도로"
    },
    {
      "start": 427.78,
      "end": 429.24,
      "text": "질문을 하는 장면이 있었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 429.24,
      "end": 429.84,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 430.08,
      "end": 430.98,
      "text": "Why me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 431.22,
      "end": 432.32,
      "text": "Why that money?"
    },
    {
      "start": 432.56,
      "end": 433.8,
      "text": "Yeah, and she also said"
    },
    {
      "start": 433.8,
      "end": 435.44,
      "text": "Teresa didn't care about"
    },
    {
      "start": 435.44,
      "end": 436.8,
      "text": "the orphanage"
    },
    {
      "start": 436.8,
      "end": 438.7,
      "text": "Yes, she tried to explain"
    },
    {
      "start": 438.7,
      "end": 439.88,
      "text": "the orphan situation"
    },
    {
      "start": 439.88,
      "end": 440.22,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 440.22,
      "end": 442.26,
      "text": "But Teresa did not seem interested"
    },
    {
      "start": 442.26,
      "end": 443.86,
      "text": "Oh, and just had interest"
    },
    {
      "start": 443.86,
      "end": 444.86,
      "text": "in her business"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.86,
      "end": 445.28,
      "text": "Business"
    },
    {
      "start": 445.28,
      "end": 446.62,
      "text": "Let's talk business"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.62,
      "end": 446.96,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.96,
      "end": 448.4,
      "text": "My business is this"
    },
    {
      "start": 448.4,
      "end": 449.9,
      "text": "I don't know about"
    },
    {
      "start": 449.9,
      "end": 451.1,
      "text": "the Indian orphanage"
    },
    {
      "start": 451.1,
      "end": 452.34,
      "text": "But I'm giving you money"
    },
    {
      "start": 452.34,
      "end": 453.38,
      "text": "Take the money"
    },
    {
      "start": 453.38,
      "end": 455.0,
      "text": "아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 455.0,
      "end": 456.62,
      "text": "자, 지금 오스카와"
    },
    {
      "start": 456.62,
      "end": 458.16,
      "text": "그리고 이자벨의"
    },
    {
      "start": 458.16,
      "end": 459.38,
      "text": "대화를 들어보면"
    },
    {
      "start": 459.38,
      "end": 461.04,
      "text": "둘이서 왠지 좀"
    },
    {
      "start": 461.04,
      "end": 462.18,
      "text": "They are in a same boat"
    },
    {
      "start": 462.18,
      "end": 463.92,
      "text": "이런 상황인 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 463.92,
      "end": 464.92,
      "text": "He doesn't know either"
    },
    {
      "start": 464.92,
      "end": 466.46,
      "text": "He's like, my wife?"
    },
    {
      "start": 466.52,
      "end": 467.16,
      "text": "I don't know"
    },
    {
      "start": 467.16,
      "end": 470.16,
      "text": "나도 요즘에 우리 와이프가"
    },
    {
      "start": 470.16,
      "end": 470.92,
      "text": "좀 이상하다 했어"
    },
    {
      "start": 470.92,
      "end": 472.4,
      "text": "막 이런 이야기가 나오잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 472.4,
      "end": 473.9,
      "text": "남편으로서 충분히"
    },
    {
      "start": 473.9,
      "end": 474.82,
      "text": "이럴 수 있는 상황"
    },
    {
      "start": 474.82,
      "end": 475.16,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.16,
      "end": 476.64,
      "text": "I don't know why she said that"
    },
    {
      "start": 476.64,
      "end": 478.24,
      "text": "I don't know why she's acting like that"
    },
    {
      "start": 478.24,
      "end": 479.24,
      "text": "Talk to her"
    },
    {
      "start": 479.24,
      "end": 479.7,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 479.7,
      "end": 480.64,
      "text": "자, 먼저"
    },
    {
      "start": 480.64,
      "end": 482.46,
      "text": "이해를 돕기 위한 표현들"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.46,
      "end": 483.24,
      "text": "알아볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 483.9,
      "end": 485.2,
      "text": "Money and principles"
    },
    {
      "start": 485.2,
      "end": 487.06,
      "text": "Money and principles"
    },
    {
      "start": 487.06,
      "end": 489.4,
      "text": "돈과 원칙들"
    },
    {
      "start": 489.4,
      "end": 490.36,
      "text": "이라는 의미입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 490.36,
      "end": 493.08,
      "text": "Idiotic, idealist"
    },
    {
      "start": 493.08,
      "end": 495.16,
      "text": "원래 idealist라고 하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 495.16,
      "end": 496.58,
      "text": "약간 positive 하지 않나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 496.98,
      "end": 499.5,
      "text": "Someone who has ideal thinking"
    },
    {
      "start": 499.5,
      "end": 500.7,
      "text": "Very positive"
    },
    {
      "start": 500.7,
      "end": 503.08,
      "text": "아주 이상적인 생각을 하는"
    },
    {
      "start": 503.08,
      "end": 504.8,
      "text": "이상가 혹은 몽상가"
    },
    {
      "start": 504.8,
      "end": 506.48,
      "text": "혹은 이상주의자라고도"
    },
    {
      "start": 506.48,
      "end": 507.58,
      "text": "해석할 수가 있는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 507.58,
      "end": 508.48,
      "text": "Optimist"
    },
    {
      "start": 508.48,
      "end": 508.8,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 508.8,
      "end": 509.52,
      "text": "이라고도 하죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 509.52,
      "end": 511.16,
      "text": "아, 낙관론자"
    },
    {
      "start": 511.16,
      "end": 511.84,
      "text": "Optimist"
    },
    {
      "start": 511.84,
      "end": 512.74,
      "text": "아, 오케이"
    },
    {
      "start": 512.74,
      "end": 514.98,
      "text": "근데 그 앞에 들렸던 표현이"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.98,
      "end": 515.7,
      "text": "Idiotic?"
    },
    {
      "start": 515.7,
      "end": 518.2,
      "text": "Oh, 이거 모순이 되는 거 아니에요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 518.2,
      "end": 518.48,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 518.48,
      "end": 519.38,
      "text": "Idiotic"
    },
    {
      "start": 519.38,
      "end": 521.28,
      "text": "If you think too ideally"
    },
    {
      "start": 521.28,
      "end": 523.82,
      "text": "you are far from reality"
    },
    {
      "start": 523.82,
      "end": 524.14,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 524.14,
      "end": 525.6,
      "text": "So people can think"
    },
    {
      "start": 525.6,
      "end": 527.02,
      "text": "you are idiotic"
    },
    {
      "start": 527.02,
      "end": 529.22,
      "text": "You are just way removed"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.22,
      "end": 531.5,
      "text": "from the reality of a situation"
    },
    {
      "start": 531.5,
      "end": 531.76,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 531.76,
      "end": 533.36,
      "text": "Idiotic idealist"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.36,
      "end": 533.8,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.8,
      "end": 535.22,
      "text": "그래서 idiotic이라는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 535.22,
      "end": 536.36,
      "text": "철자 먼저 알려드리면"
    },
    {
      "start": 536.36,
      "end": 538.78,
      "text": "I-D-I-O-T-I-C"
    },
    {
      "start": 538.78,
      "end": 539.7,
      "text": "이라는 철자인데"
    },
    {
      "start": 539.7,
      "end": 541.82,
      "text": "멍청한 바보 같은"
    },
    {
      "start": 541.82,
      "end": 542.3,
      "text": "이라는 의미였습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.3,
      "end": 543.66,
      "text": "Idiot"
    },
    {
      "start": 543.66,
      "end": 544.68,
      "text": "그 명사로"
    },
    {
      "start": 544.68,
      "end": 545.96,
      "text": "You idiot"
    },
    {
      "start": 545.96,
      "end": 547.16,
      "text": "친구끼리 막 놀릴 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.16,
      "end": 548.66,
      "text": "그렇게 이야기 종종 하잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 548.66,
      "end": 548.92,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 548.92,
      "end": 549.82,
      "text": "Yeah, with my brothers"
    },
    {
      "start": 549.82,
      "end": 551.52,
      "text": "we always called each other idiots"
    },
    {
      "start": 551.52,
      "end": 552.32,
      "text": "No, you're an idiot"
    },
    {
      "start": 552.32,
      "end": 553.28,
      "text": "Always call each other"
    },
    {
      "start": 553.28,
      "end": 554.62,
      "text": "Idiot, jerk"
    },
    {
      "start": 554.62,
      "end": 554.9,
      "text": "So funny"
    },
    {
      "start": 554.9,
      "end": 555.82,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 555.82,
      "end": 557.52,
      "text": "Those were the go-to insults"
    },
    {
      "start": 557.52,
      "end": 558.64,
      "text": "그래요"
    },
    {
      "start": 558.64,
      "end": 559.46,
      "text": "아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 559.46,
      "end": 561.52,
      "text": "Idiotic idealist라고 했으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 561.52,
      "end": 563.5,
      "text": "멍청한 몽상가"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.5,
      "end": 565.9,
      "text": "바보 같은 이상주의자라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 565.9,
      "end": 567.1,
      "text": "해석하시면 되겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 567.1,
      "end": 569.6,
      "text": "Interested in business"
    },
    {
      "start": 569.6,
      "end": 571.98,
      "text": "Interested in business"
    },
    {
      "start": 571.98,
      "end": 573.66,
      "text": "사업에 관심 있는"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.66,
      "end": 574.6,
      "text": "이라는 표현까지"
    },
    {
      "start": 574.6,
      "end": 575.52,
      "text": "점검을 해봤고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 575.52,
      "end": 577.38,
      "text": "이 내용 한 번 더 들어볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 577.38,
      "end": 579.14,
      "text": "You don't have to be poor"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.14,
      "end": 580.36,
      "text": "to have good intentions"
    },
    {
      "start": 580.36,
      "end": 581.5,
      "text": "There are people with money"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.5,
      "end": 582.56,
      "text": "and principles, okay?"
    },
    {
      "start": 582.94,
      "end": 583.26,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.14,
      "end": 585.36,
      "text": "That's not what I remember you saying"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.36,
      "end": 586.08,
      "text": "when I knew you"
    },
    {
      "start": 586.08,
      "end": 588.26,
      "text": "It's because I was an idiotic idealist"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.26,
      "end": 589.16,
      "text": "that I grew up"
    },
    {
      "start": 589.16,
      "end": 590.32,
      "text": "Did you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.3,
      "end": 591.6,
      "text": "No"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.6,
      "end": 594.6,
      "text": "Teresa doesn't care about the orphanage"
    },
    {
      "start": 594.6,
      "end": 596.14,
      "text": "She doesn't want to talk about it"
    },
    {
      "start": 596.14,
      "end": 597.5,
      "text": "She's interested in business"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.5,
      "end": 599.3,
      "text": "So what does she want?"
    },
    {
      "start": 599.3,
      "end": 601.54,
      "text": "그래도"
    },
    {
      "start": 601.54,
      "end": 602.58,
      "text": "이 오스카"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.58,
      "end": 604.46,
      "text": "남편이 이야기한 것을"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.46,
      "end": 605.54,
      "text": "처음에 듣는 순간"
    },
    {
      "start": 605.54,
      "end": 606.64,
      "text": "확실히"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.64,
      "end": 608.5,
      "text": "As Teresa's husband"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.5,
      "end": 610.3,
      "text": "he was defending her side"
    },
    {
      "start": 610.3,
      "end": 612.14,
      "text": "그래도"
    },
    {
      "start": 612.14,
      "end": 614.42,
      "text": "남의 편은 아니었구나"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.42,
      "end": 615.64,
      "text": "남편?"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.78,
      "end": 616.7,
      "text": "남의 편이 아닙니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 616.7,
      "end": 617.82,
      "text": "네, 이와 같이"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.82,
      "end": 618.7,
      "text": "Look at this guy"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.7,
      "end": 620.32,
      "text": "아내 편을 들어주는"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.32,
      "end": 622.66,
      "text": "아주 훈훈한 문장이었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.66,
      "end": 623.76,
      "text": "He's a good husband"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.76,
      "end": 624.22,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.22,
      "end": 625.32,
      "text": "Faithful to his wife"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.32,
      "end": 627.08,
      "text": "And always takes his wife's side"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.08,
      "end": 627.42,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.42,
      "end": 628.62,
      "text": "Even though he doesn't understand"
    },
    {
      "start": 628.62,
      "end": 629.7,
      "text": "what she's doing himself"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.7,
      "end": 630.46,
      "text": "그게 중요하죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 630.46,
      "end": 632.16,
      "text": "이해가 안 될지라도"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.16,
      "end": 634.68,
      "text": "일단 아내의 편을 들어주는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 634.68,
      "end": 635.62,
      "text": "아주 좋습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 635.62,
      "end": 636.84,
      "text": "아, 그런 남편이 있나봐요"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.84,
      "end": 637.08,
      "text": "네?"
    },
    {
      "start": 637.26,
      "end": 637.94,
      "text": "항상 내 편"
    },
    {
      "start": 637.94,
      "end": 638.16,
      "text": "어?"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.36,
      "end": 638.62,
      "text": "네?"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.74,
      "end": 639.54,
      "text": "내 편 들어주는"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.54,
      "end": 640.46,
      "text": "누구요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.08,
      "end": 642.22,
      "text": "남의 편인가?"
    },
    {
      "start": 642.26,
      "end": 643.64,
      "text": "누구 이야기를 하는 것인지"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.64,
      "end": 645.4,
      "text": "자, 오스카"
    },
    {
      "start": 645.4,
      "end": 647.68,
      "text": "남편이 뭐라고 했는지 알아볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 647.68,
      "end": 649.02,
      "text": "You don't have to be poor"
    },
    {
      "start": 649.02,
      "end": 650.38,
      "text": "to have good intentions"
    },
    {
      "start": 650.38,
      "end": 652.38,
      "text": "You don't have to be poor"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.38,
      "end": 654.24,
      "text": "to have good intentions"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.24,
      "end": 655.86,
      "text": "좋은 의도"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.86,
      "end": 657.94,
      "text": "선한 의도를 가지기 위해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 657.94,
      "end": 660.74,
      "text": "꼭 가난할 필요는 없잖아"
    },
    {
      "start": 660.74,
      "end": 661.88,
      "text": "라는 의미입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 661.88,
      "end": 663.8,
      "text": "That's a, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 663.8,
      "end": 666.0,
      "text": "Just because you have a lot of money"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.0,
      "end": 668.48,
      "text": "doesn't mean your intentions are bad"
    },
    {
      "start": 668.48,
      "end": 670.24,
      "text": "or corrupted, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 670.76,
      "end": 671.52,
      "text": "그런 거는 약간"
    },
    {
      "start": 671.52,
      "end": 673.72,
      "text": "sort of prejudice가 될 수가 있겠죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.72,
      "end": 674.66,
      "text": "It's, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 674.66,
      "end": 676.06,
      "text": "It's a 편견"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.06,
      "end": 678.06,
      "text": "선입견 같은 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.06,
      "end": 679.12,
      "text": "Sometimes it's true"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.12,
      "end": 679.54,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.54,
      "end": 680.48,
      "text": "Sometimes"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.48,
      "end": 683.53,
      "text": "There are people with money"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.53,
      "end": 685.21,
      "text": "and principles, okay?"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.75,
      "end": 687.15,
      "text": "There are people with money"
    },
    {
      "start": 687.15,
      "end": 688.65,
      "text": "and principles, okay?"
    },
    {
      "start": 689.09,
      "end": 690.65,
      "text": "돈과 원칙들"
    },
    {
      "start": 690.65,
      "end": 692.99,
      "text": "이 두 개 다 가지고 있는 사람들도"
    },
    {
      "start": 692.99,
      "end": 693.83,
      "text": "많이 있어"
    },
    {
      "start": 693.83,
      "end": 694.77,
      "text": "라는 의미입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.77,
      "end": 695.31,
      "text": "See, see?"
    },
    {
      "start": 695.51,
      "end": 696.67,
      "text": "It is a stereotype"
    },
    {
      "start": 696.67,
      "end": 697.23,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 697.23,
      "end": 698.41,
      "text": "You can have both"
    },
    {
      "start": 698.41,
      "end": 699.27,
      "text": "A lot of money"
    },
    {
      "start": 699.27,
      "end": 701.41,
      "text": "and good moral principles"
    },
    {
      "start": 701.41,
      "end": 701.63,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 701.63,
      "end": 703.4,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 704.24,
      "end": 704.56,
      "text": "정말?"
    },
    {
      "start": 705.04,
      "end": 705.48,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 705.7,
      "end": 706.32,
      "text": "과연 그럴까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 706.32,
      "end": 707.44,
      "text": "라는 의도였습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 707.44,
      "end": 709.08,
      "text": "She sounds a little doubtful"
    },
    {
      "start": 709.08,
      "end": 709.4,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 709.4,
      "end": 711.32,
      "text": "That's not what I remember"
    },
    {
      "start": 711.32,
      "end": 712.04,
      "text": "you saying"
    },
    {
      "start": 712.04,
      "end": 713.28,
      "text": "when I knew you"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.28,
      "end": 715.24,
      "text": "That's not what I remember"
    },
    {
      "start": 715.24,
      "end": 716.08,
      "text": "you saying"
    },
    {
      "start": 716.08,
      "end": 717.32,
      "text": "when I knew you"
    },
    {
      "start": 717.32,
      "end": 718.14,
      "text": "아, 변했구나"
    },
    {
      "start": 718.14,
      "end": 718.96,
      "text": "와우"
    },
    {
      "start": 718.96,
      "end": 719.46,
      "text": "변했어"
    },
    {
      "start": 719.46,
      "end": 720.66,
      "text": "You changed"
    },
    {
      "start": 720.66,
      "end": 722.16,
      "text": "내가 알던 당신은"
    },
    {
      "start": 722.16,
      "end": 723.74,
      "text": "그렇게 말하지 않았는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 723.74,
      "end": 724.44,
      "text": "말이지"
    },
    {
      "start": 724.44,
      "end": 725.38,
      "text": "이라는 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 725.38,
      "end": 726.38,
      "text": "When he was younger"
    },
    {
      "start": 726.38,
      "end": 727.52,
      "text": "a long time ago"
    },
    {
      "start": 727.52,
      "end": 729.96,
      "text": "That's because"
    },
    {
      "start": 729.96,
      "end": 732.2,
      "text": "I was an idiotic idealist"
    },
    {
      "start": 732.2,
      "end": 733.7,
      "text": "but I grew up"
    },
    {
      "start": 733.7,
      "end": 734.54,
      "text": "와우"
    },
    {
      "start": 734.54,
      "end": 736.16,
      "text": "지금 자기 비판하는 건가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 736.54,
      "end": 737.74,
      "text": "That's because"
    },
    {
      "start": 737.74,
      "end": 740.0,
      "text": "I was an idiotic idealist"
    },
    {
      "start": 740.0,
      "end": 741.16,
      "text": "but I grew up"
    },
    {
      "start": 741.16,
      "end": 741.8,
      "text": "이라고 했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 741.8,
      "end": 743.52,
      "text": "왜냐하면 내가"
    },
    {
      "start": 743.52,
      "end": 744.38,
      "text": "그 당시에"
    },
    {
      "start": 744.38,
      "end": 746.96,
      "text": "멍청한 이상주의자였으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 746.96,
      "end": 748.72,
      "text": "but I grew up"
    },
    {
      "start": 748.72,
      "end": 749.6,
      "text": "하지만 난"
    },
    {
      "start": 749.6,
      "end": 750.72,
      "text": "성장했어"
    },
    {
      "start": 750.72,
      "end": 751.96,
      "text": "철들었지"
    },
    {
      "start": 751.96,
      "end": 753.28,
      "text": "Yeah, I matured"
    },
    {
      "start": 753.28,
      "end": 754.06,
      "text": "Back then"
    },
    {
      "start": 754.06,
      "end": 755.2,
      "text": "I had a good heart"
    },
    {
      "start": 755.2,
      "end": 756.4,
      "text": "full of passion"
    },
    {
      "start": 756.4,
      "end": 758.4,
      "text": "오, 우연히 느낀 건데"
    },
    {
      "start": 758.4,
      "end": 762.42,
      "text": "I matured"
    },
    {
      "start": 762.42,
      "end": 762.98,
      "text": "이라고 했잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 762.98,
      "end": 763.62,
      "text": "I matured"
    },
    {
      "start": 763.62,
      "end": 764.78,
      "text": "Yeah, I matured"
    },
    {
      "start": 764.78,
      "end": 765.34,
      "text": "라고 했는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 765.34,
      "end": 766.88,
      "text": "이 철들었다"
    },
    {
      "start": 766.88,
      "end": 768.04,
      "text": "아, 철"
    },
    {
      "start": 768.04,
      "end": 769.06,
      "text": "그 끝부분"
    },
    {
      "start": 769.06,
      "end": 769.64,
      "text": "철"
    },
    {
      "start": 769.64,
      "end": 770.34,
      "text": "아, 발음이"
    },
    {
      "start": 770.34,
      "end": 771.06,
      "text": "와우"
    },
    {
      "start": 771.06,
      "end": 773.3,
      "text": "Very 예리한"
    },
    {
      "start": 773.3,
      "end": 773.84,
      "text": "죄송합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 773.84,
      "end": 774.52,
      "text": "관찰"
    },
    {
      "start": 774.52,
      "end": 776.78,
      "text": "어떻게든 끼워 맞춰보려고"
    },
    {
      "start": 776.78,
      "end": 777.54,
      "text": "해봤어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 777.54,
      "end": 778.12,
      "text": "아, 좋았어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 778.12,
      "end": 780.02,
      "text": "예, 기억에 남으면 좋겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 780.02,
      "end": 780.98,
      "text": "I'm matured"
    },
    {
      "start": 780.98,
      "end": 781.16,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 781.16,
      "end": 782.24,
      "text": "Good expression"
    },
    {
      "start": 782.24,
      "end": 783.28,
      "text": "철, 철"
    },
    {
      "start": 783.28,
      "end": 783.88,
      "text": "철"
    },
    {
      "start": 783.88,
      "end": 786.43,
      "text": "But I grew up"
    },
    {
      "start": 786.43,
      "end": 786.93,
      "text": "이것도 좋아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 786.93,
      "end": 787.13,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 787.13,
      "end": 787.97,
      "text": "I grew up"
    },
    {
      "start": 787.97,
      "end": 789.49,
      "text": "Did you"
    },
    {
      "start": 789.49,
      "end": 790.19,
      "text": "Did you"
    },
    {
      "start": 790.19,
      "end": 791.57,
      "text": "당신은"
    },
    {
      "start": 791.57,
      "end": 792.77,
      "text": "너는 철들었니?"
    },
    {
      "start": 792.93,
      "end": 794.07,
      "text": "라는 의도가 되겠네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 794.07,
      "end": 794.63,
      "text": "컸니?"
    },
    {
      "start": 794.63,
      "end": 795.95,
      "text": "Did you grow up?"
    },
    {
      "start": 795.99,
